task.summary: Default task
Added first version of cell_builder
Fixed path to demo_cell in cell_builder
Changed format for mechanisms in Cell.create and in demo neuron files
Changed variable name filename to model_dir in class Cell()

Set celsius in hoc
Before celsius had no effect on runs of the cell.

Changed parameters: l, ra for Section to upper case
NEURON parameters need to have the same name in python in order to be applied.

Changed demo directory
Now demo is directly in folder cell_fitting.

New function in Class Cell: get_attr()
Cell.get_attr(self,keys) allows the access of an attribute of Cell by a list of keys (same as used for update_attr)
Changed :type specifications to lower case for python build-in types

New function in Section Class: play_current
The function play_current can be used to play a vector containing the current at each time step into a cell during a simulation.

First version of the optimizer
Optimizer can be used for fitting cells with evoluationary multi-objective optimization to experimental data.
Commit .idea file from pycharm
Add demo cells and data for testing and demonstrating code
Added .gitignore

Changed init of Section
Sections are now initialized with the parameter geom instead of L, diam to allow to change between the L, diam and the pt3dadd representation of the geometry.

Changed Section init and added test function test_morph
Section was changed to allow the definition of morphology by either L and diam or by 3D and diam coordinates. The function test_morph plots the morphology of a cell.

Changed update_attr() method of Cell
The method update_attr() is now able to add new paths to params defined by keys if they did not existed yet.
Method substitute_section as method from Cell

Fixed Bug generating candidate with 1 variable When bounds were given per variable but there was just one variable generator was jumping into the wrong condition and returning a nested list as a candidate. Changing order of if conditions fixed the problem.
Fixed Bug Checks now whether bounds are given as float number or have len.
Fixed Bug Now bounds are first checked if length 1, then if they are iterable in which case you use the content as bounds.
Added functions to make comparable optimization for the different algorithms. Problem does now carry a cell (faster than to create on every evaluation).
Added histogram and 2d plot of performance of different parameters (to see which ones are easier to analyze)
Exchanged generator in inspired_extension and added testing suite
Made individuals_observer independent of pandas, changed candidate representation to white space separated numbers without square brackets and switched order of columns for better readability
Added sorting
Abstract implementation of Problem and NormalizedProblem
Interface for the heka_reader to easily get data from heka patchmaster .dat files
Computes the capacitance of a cell from the hypTester protocol (small negative step current)
Refactored optimization mainly into optimization_settings, algorithm_settings and fitter
To select and save traces from .dat files with the hekareader
Organized fitness landscape analysis
Some changes on fitnesslandscape analysis e.g. computation of minima
Some useful functions
tries to find best fitness landscape by linear regression
Function to combine different fitness landscapes linearly
made search for minima in 2d faster
Changed implementation of get_local_minima_2d to greatly improve speed
Changed implementation of get_local_minima_2d to greatly improve speed
Updated handtuner
Corrected get_DAP_deflection: now gives the absolute value Updated example wit units
Uses now matplotlib FigureCanvas and NavigationToolbar for plots
Variables are now initialized to their lower bound
Fixed unit conversion
update handtuner
